{"title":"xshell连接linux虚拟机系统","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.037Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/xshell连接linux虚拟机系统","updated":"2023-07-28T09:11:44.864Z","content":"<h1 id=\"xshell连接linux虚拟机系统\"><strong>xshell连接linux虚拟机系统</strong><a title=\"#xshell连接linux虚拟机系统\" href=\"#xshell连接linux虚拟机系统\"></a></h1>\n<p>1、首先<a href=\"https://xshell.en.softonic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">下载xshell，https://xshell.en.softonic.com/</a></p>\n<p>2、在虚拟机终端输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ifconfig</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看输出的ip地址<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/efbde0b0d0e54bbf97d28a1f8fa80ddb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n这里我们取第一个<code>192.168.205.128</code>，每个人地址可能不一样，取你自己的地址即可</p>\n<p>3、在xshell中新建会话，输入刚刚的IP地址<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c1017f3071ff48baa6b2253ca88a0d22.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n点击确定后输入你linux主机的用户名和密码即可连接<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/98be5268896648c6a262c713b171504e.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/23e02ea94b3449c3b41bf8524603decf.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5d59408292af460f9feeca2878c88556.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\nPs：连接失败时请确认<br>\n1、虚拟机22端口开发<br>\n2、虚拟机已安装ssh服务，并确保ssh服务正在运行<br>\n3、虚拟机防火墙已关闭</p>\n","prev":{"title":"解决ssh_exchange_identification_ read_ Connection reset by peer","link":"2023/07/28/解决ssh_exchange_identification_ read_ Connection reset by peer"},"next":{"title":"多机docker部署fisco-bcos区块链","link":"2023/07/28/多机docker部署fisco-bcos区块链"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/xshell连接linux虚拟机系统/","toc":[{"id":"xshell连接linux虚拟机系统","title":"xshell连接linux虚拟机系统","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"301 字约 2 分钟"}